1953;;Always a Bride;;British;;Ralph Smart;;Peggy Cummins, Terence Morgan;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Always_a_Bride_(1953_film);;A British father and daughter work a confidence trick up and down the luxury hotels of the French Riviera by posing as a newly married couple. Trouble begins, however, when the daughter falls in love with a tax investigator.